%% Diagram: Lamport Clock Trace
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant P1 as P1 (L=0)
    participant P2 as P2 (L=0)
    participant P3 as P3 (L=0)

    Note over P1: local event<br/>L=1
    P1->>P2: m1 (ts=2)
    Note over P2: recv m1<br/>L=max(0,2)+1=3
    P2->>P3: m2 (ts=4)
    Note over P3: recv m2<br/>L=max(0,4)+1=5
    Note over P1: local event<br/>L=3
    P3->>P1: m3 (ts=6)
    Note over P1: recv m3<br/>L=max(3,6)+1=7

    Note right of P3: A→B implies L(A)<L(B).<br/>The converse does not hold:<br/>independent events can still<br/>get ordered timestamps.
